                            <comment id="14791838" author="blerer" created="Thu, 17 Sep 2015 09:32:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The patch fix the view check and add a unit test to verify the behaviour.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Waiting for CI results.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14802751" author="iamaleksey" created="Thu, 17 Sep 2015 11:07:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This works, but would be better to just switch&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;CFMetaData cfm = ksm.tables.getNullable(columnFamily());
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;with&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;CFMetaData cfm = ksm.getTableOrViewNullable(columnFamily());
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;instead.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14802820" author="iamaleksey" created="Thu, 17 Sep 2015 12:07:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;v2 +1.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
